reviewText: What a great way to sample workouts from different trainers before investing in a full program. Beachbody should make a new one to include Chalean Extreme, Focus T25, Asylum, P90X3 and 21 Day Fix.
Love this tape! Change to a different trainer or type of training - all on the same tape! Why didn't someone think of this sooner?
I guess I didn't read the description carefully enough. This is just a promo for all their different workouts.. not very good. I basically paid for one of their advertisements.
